  "prompt": "What are some good dance club songs?",
  "response": "Selecting good dance club songs can depend on personal taste and the current trends in music. Here are some popular choices that have been known to get people moving:\n\n1. \"Levitating\" - Dua Lipa\n2. \"Blinding Lights\" - The Weeknd\n3. \"Don't Start Now\" - Dua Lipa\n4. \"Rain On Me\" - Lady Gaga & Ariana Grande\n5. \"Uptown Funk\" - Mark Ronson ft. Bruno Mars\n6. \"Dance Monkey\" - Tones and I\n7. \"Break My Heart\" - Dua Lipa\n8. \"Peaches\" - Justin Bieber ft. Daniel Caesar & Giveon\n9. \"Staying Alive\" - DJ Khaled ft. Drake & Lil Baby\n10. \"Head & Heart\" - Joel Corry ft. MNEK\n11. \"Butter\" - BTS\n12. \"On The Floor\" - Jennifer Lopez ft. Pitbull\n13. \"Taki Taki\" - DJ Snake ft. Selena Gomez, Ozuna & Cardi B\n14. \"Turn Down for What\" - DJ Snake & Lil Jon\n15. \"Shape of You\" - Ed Sheeran\n\nThese songs have catchy beats and rhythms that are perfect for dancing and have been popular in clubs around the world.",
